sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Browser as Web Browser
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NotebookCtrl as Notebook Controller
    participant Notebook as Jupyter Notebook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>9090/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Workflow 1: Data Scientist Onboarding to Model Deployment

    User->>Browser: Access Dashboard URL
    Browser->>Dashboard: HTTPS/443
    Dashboard->>OAuth: Redirect for authentication<br/>Bearer Token
    OAuth-->>Dashboard: OAuth Token
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Dashboard UI

    User->>Dashboard: Create Data Science Project
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Namespace<br/>POST /api/v1/namespaces<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: Namespace created

    User->>Dashboard: Launch Jupyter Notebook
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>POST /apis/kubeflow.org/v1/namespaces/{ns}/notebooks<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch event
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet, Route, OAuth proxy<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Resources created

    User->>Notebook: Access notebook via Route<br/>HTTPS/443 OAuth
    Notebook-->>User: JupyterLab interface

    User->>Notebook: Develop model, train locally
    Notebook->>S3: Download datasets<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM
    S3-->>Notebook: Dataset files

    User->>Notebook: Register model in registry
    Notebook->>ModelReg: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>gRPC/9090 mTLS Bearer Token
    ModelReg-->>Notebook: Model registered

    User->>Dashboard: Create InferenceService
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>POST /apis/serving.kserve.io/v1beta1/namespaces/{ns}/inferenceservices<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>KServe: Watch event
    KServe->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>Bearer Token
    KServe->>Predictor: Deploy with storage-initializer
    Predictor->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM
    S3-->>Predictor: Model files
    KServe->>K8sAPI: Create Route, VirtualService, AuthConfig<br/>Bearer Token

    Note over User,S3: Inference Request Flow

    User->>Istio: POST https://{model-url}/v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    Istio->>Istio: Authorize via Authorino<br/>Kubernetes Token Review
    Istio->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run inference
    Predictor-->>Istio: Prediction JSON
    Istio-->>User: HTTPS Response
